name: 美少女万華鏡－忘れな草と永遠の少女－沢渡 雫 / Bishojo Mangekyo－Wasurenagusa To Eien No Shoujo－ Sawatari Shizuku / 美少女万华镜－勿忘草与永远的少女－ 沢渡雫
description:
2023,04,20 v2.0

三个衣服能正常画出来了

睡衣：Sawatari-Shizuku-ns, pink nightshirt

私服：Sawatari-Shizuku-pc, white dress

体操服：Sawatari-Shizuku-pl, bodysuit

Google Translate:

The three clothes can be drawn normally

Pajamas: Sawatari-Shizuku-ns, pink nightshirt

Private server: Sawatari-Shizuku-pc, white dress

Gym uniform: Sawatari-Shizuku-pl, bodysuit

OLD v1.0

懒了，不想写东西

Sawatari Shizuku.

后面这些衣服tag感觉没起作用。

dress, swimsuit, nightshirt, print leotard, school uniform, nude.

就当我没练衣服吧

Google Translate:

I'm lazy, I don't want to write

Sawatari Shizuku.

The latter prompts for clothes don't seem to work.

dress, swimsuit, nightshirt, print leotard, school uniform, nude.

Just pretend I don't have training clothes
